title: The Lesser of Two Crab Claws, Part 1
itunes:title: The Lesser of Two Crab Claws, Part 1
description:
In this episode of Stuff to Blow Your Mind, Robert and Joe discuss biological asymmetry in the natural world – including various examples of organisms in which side A doesn’t quite match up with side B.
